org.zaproxy.zap.extension.ext

Class ExtensionParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.parosproxy.paros.common.AbstractParam
      • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.ext.ExtensionParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class ExtensionParam
extends AbstractParam
    Manages the extensions' configurations saved in the configuration file.

    It allows to change, programmatically, the extensions' enabled state.

    Since:
    2.5.0

      • isExtensionEnabled

        public boolean isExtensionEnabled(String extensionName)
        Tells whether or not the extension with the given name is enabled.

        Extensions are enabled by default.

        Parameters:
        extensionName - the name of the extension to check.
        Returns:
        true if extension is enabled, false otherwise.

        2.6.0
